title: Rum and raisin brownies
ingredients: ['80g raisins', '3 tablespoons rum', '150ml whipping cream', '170g dark chocolate chips', '85g plain flour', '75g light brown soft sugar', '2 tablespoons cocoa powder', '1/4 teaspoon baking powder', '1/3 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '2 eggs', '80g chopped toasted pecans']
